Jacqueline Kim https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacqueline_Kim 0 Jacqueline Joan Kim (born March 31, 1965) is an American writer, actress, filmmaker and composer. She was nominated for a FIND Independent Spirit award for Best Supporting Actress in the film, Charlotte Sometimes.
